body:
### Not Every Command Is a Tag!
Ahh, sorry about that. Had to get it out of my system. Anyway, welcome to Spectra's website. Right now it's pretty bare, but in future I hope to have some nice help files, tutorials, and more!

### **Spectra** by jagrosh
**Spectra** is a multi-purpose, for-fun and for-utility [Discord](https://discordapp.com) bot. It has a lot of features, including profiles, private channel management, reminders, web/video/image searches, chat cleaning, role management, moderation tools, and of course, tags and tag scripting (jagtagâ„¢). To find out more, join jagrosh's Bots Server, [Spectra Lounge](https://discord.gg/0p9LSGoRLu6Pet0k). Feel free to contact @jagrosh with any questions, concerns, bug reports, feature requests, or feedback. I'll get back to you as soon as I can!
